含happy: elns watching people making popcorn like that was one of the happiest things in my childhood. back then we had very few snacks or food. the popcorn guy walked town to town. when he came to our neighborhood we were really happy. we brought our own rice or corn kernel and only paid him several cents for making popcorn. he roasted his tightly sealed pot over fire. at the end he released the lid and it made a super loud sound. and we the children just jumped away with laughter.
含happy中文翻译: Elns看着人们做爆米花的人是我童年时代最快乐的事情之一。那时我们有很少的小吃或食物。爆米花的家伙走到城镇。当他来到我们附近时，我们真的很高兴。我们带来了自己的米饭或玉米仁，只付了他的几分钱来制作爆米花。他在火上烤了紧密密封的锅。最后，他释放了盖子，它发出了超大的声音。我们的孩子们只是大笑起来。
